    "question": "What is Pythagorean theorem?",
    "correctAnswer": "a^2 + b^2 = c^2 for right triangle legs a,b hypotenuse c",
    "incorrectAnswers": [
      "a+b=c",
      "a^2=b^2+c^2 always",
      "c=a+b"
    ],
    "explanation": "Applies only to right triangles.",
